      <title>黑客拍卖被盗的 LendingTree 消费者数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/hackers-auction-off-stolen-lendingtree-consumers-information</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在 LendingTree Inc. 子公司 QuoteWizard 检测到 Snowflake Inc. 托管的云数据库受到未经授权的访问后，黑客正在出售有关该公司消费者的数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/hackers-auction-off-stolen-lendingtree-consumers-information</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 20:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CDK 告知汽车经销商其系统可能离线数天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/car-dealers-are-idle-across-the-us-after-second-cyberattack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CDK Global 是数千家汽车经销商运营门店所依赖的软件提供商，在遭受第二次重大网络攻击后，美国各地的汽车零售商可能会暂停服务数天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/car-dealers-are-idle-across-the-us-after-second-cyberattack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:49:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
